Package: URBANmetRics
Title: Urban Structure Metrics from OpenStreetMap
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Franka", "L.", email = "fhlou16@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a modular workflow to extract urban structures 
    (buildings, green spaces, transport infrastructure) from OpenStreetMap, 
    compute geometry-based metrics, and combine them into an integrated 
    urban index. The package currently includes structure extraction, 
    classification, metric computation, and index calculation.
